\c 146 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 146\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Isa Gargaarsi Biraa Dhufu Irra Abdii Kaa'achuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Waaqayyoon jajadhu, yaa lubbuu ko.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ani jireenya koo guutuu Waaqayyoon nan jajadha, hamman jirutti jajuu Waaqayyo koo nan faarfadha!
\m \bd 3\bd* Amanannaa keessan gurguddoota irra, ilmaan namaa warra gargaarsi bira hin jirre irras hin kaa'atinaa.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yeroo hafuurri isaa keessaa baatu, inni deebi'ee biyyoo in ta'a; guyyuma sanas akeeki isaa in bada.
\m \bd 5\bd* Namni, Waaqayyo inni kan Yaaqoob gargaarsa isaa ta'eef, abdii isaas Waaqayyo isaa goofticha irra inni kaa'ate haa gammadu.
\m \bd 6\bd* Gooftichi isa bantii waaqaa fi lafa, galaanaa fi wanta isaan keessa jirus uumee dha; inni bara baraan amanamummaa in eega.
\m \bd 7\bd* Inni warra cunqurfamaniif dhugaa in baasa; warra beela'aniifis soora in kenna; Waaqayyo warra hidhaman hiikee gad in dhiisa.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo jaamotaaf agartuu isaanii in deebisa; Waaqayyo warra gad deebi'an ol in kaasa; Waaqayyo warra qajeelota in jaallata.
\m \bd 9\bd* Waaqayyo galaa biyya ormaa in eega; inni ijoollee abbaan irra hin jirree fi haadha hiyyeessaa in jiraachisa; karaa warra jal'ootaa garuu irraa in kaachisa.
\m \bd 10\bd* Yaa Xiyoon, Waaqayyo kee gooftichi, dhalootaa hamma dhalootaatti, bara baraan in mo'a! Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
